		</p><p>
			<tt>glGet</tt> with argument <tt>GL_MAX_PIXEL_MAP_TABLE</tt>
		</p></div><div class="refsect1" lang="en"><a name="glGetPixelMap.3G-see_also"/><h2>See Also</h2><p>
